OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784895503
OL,3,CSouthport killer 'manipulating system'
OL,4,Cafter psychiatric hospital transfer
OL,6,FA lawyer for the families of the
OL,7,Fchildren murdered by the Southport
OL,8,Fkiller has said his transfer from
OL,9,Fprison to a high security psychiatric
OL,10,Fhospital is another attempt by him to
OL,11,F"manipulate the system".
OL,13,FNow 19, the killer, referred to as AR,
OL,14,Fwas given a life sentence for the
OL,15,Fmurders of Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,16,Fnine; Bebe King, six; and Elsie Dot
OL,17,FStancombe, seven, and the attempted
OL,18,Fmurder of eight other children and two
OL,19,Fadults.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
