OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784895503
OL,3,CSouthport killer 'manipulating system'
OL,4,Cafter psychiatric hospital transfer
OL,6,FIt will be two years since he carried
OL,7,Fout the attack at a Taylor Swift-
OL,8,Fthemed dance class on 29 July 2024.
OL,10,FThe Ministry of Justice (MoJ) has
OL,11,Fconfirmed officials approved the
OL,12,Ftransfer to Broadmoor Psychiatric
OL,13,FHospital on behalf of ministers, but a
OL,14,Fspokesperson for the department
OL,15,Fstressed it does not alter the
OL,16,Fkiller's 52-year sentence.
OL,18,FBut solicitor Chris Walker, who is
OL,19,Frepresenting the three bereaved
OL,20,Ffamilies, believes AR is "attempting,
OL,21,Fonce again, to manipulate the system."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784895503
OL,3,CSouthport killer 'manipulating system'
OL,4,Cafter psychiatric hospital transfer
OL,6,FIn a statement, he said: "The three
OL,7,Ffamilies we represent have been made
OL,8,Faware of this development in the last
OL,9,F48 hours and it is safe to say that
OL,10,Fwhilst this news would devastate them
OL,11,Fat any time, the fact that this has
OL,12,Foccurred as we approach the second
OL,13,Fanniversary in our view is another
OL,14,Fmove by AR who would appear to be
OL,15,Fattempting, once again, to manipulate
OL,16,Fthe system.
OL,26,@nD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784895503
OL,3,CSouthport killer 'manipulating system'
OL,4,Cafter psychiatric hospital transfer
OL,6,F"We have been given the barest of
OL,7,Fdetails and whilst we are supporting
OL,8,Fthe families through this we are
OL,9,Furgently seeking a meeting with the
OL,10,Fappropriate authorities to understand
OL,11,Fthe situation before commenting
OL,12,Ffurther."
OL,14,FThe move to Broadmoor high security
OL,15,Fhospital from the category A prison
OL,16,FBelmarsh was first reported by the
OL,17,FGuardian on 23 July.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
