FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784895503
OL,3,CSouthport killer 'manipulating system'
OL,4,Cafter psychiatric hospital transfer
OL,6,FOffenders who present an increased
OL,7,Frisk, and cannot be managed safely in
OL,8,Fa prison environment because of mental
OL,9,Fdisorders, can be moved to secure
OL,10,Fpsychiatric units.
OL,12,FThe MOJ spokesperson said: "The
OL,13,Ffamilies of those murdered and injured
OL,14,Fin Southport will be in this country's
OL,15,Fheart forever and our thoughts remain
OL,16,Fwith them.
OL,26,@tD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
