OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1784895503
OL,3,CSouthport killer 'manipulating system'
OL,4,Cafter psychiatric hospital transfer
OL,6,F"Any decision to transfer an offender
OL,7,Fis made following an independent,
OL,8,Fclinical assessment, under the Mental
OL,9,FHealth Act. Following rigorous
OL,10,Fsecurity checks, the offender has been
OL,11,Ftransferred to a high-security
OL,12,Fpsychiatric unit, where he will remain
OL,13,Funtil assessed fit to return to prison.
OL,15,F"Officials have approved this
OL,16,Ftransfer, on behalf of Ministers. This
OL,17,Ftransfer does not change his sentence
OL,18,F` which remains at 52 years ` and of
OL,19,Fwhich he will serve every single day."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@fO]
